[dbo].[NewRegularProcedure].definition:
CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[NewRegularProcedure]
(
    @name varchar(255)
)
AS
BEGIN
    SELECT @name
END

[dbo].[NewEncryptedProcedure].definition:
CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[NewEncryptedProcedure]
(
    @name varchar(255)
)
WITH ENCRYPTION
AS
BEGIN
    SELECT @name
END
